Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,认知障碍的魔导书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那个方便的魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想教给康娜和伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔还真是为朋友着想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算你夸我  我也只会给你我的血肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用害羞啊  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:40.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么魔法式的文字排列
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:48.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟我们公司开发的编程语言…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很相似对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为那就是由我们魔法使创作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你对我们这边有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也到该好奇的时候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,您说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:14.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,关于托尔来到这个世界的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那种事就由她本人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就听她的家人讲讲如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为什么您会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和这个男人认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:44.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我从他那里了解托尔的近况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你既然来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就代表你想要听我讲话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:51.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是之后我也会听托尔自己说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无休止的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,汇聚了一些战力就火拼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:15.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只有不断消耗的持久战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,战斗的理由是要打倒神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让世界回归没有调停者的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我们因为厌恶被管制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以才露出獠牙争取自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最开始龙族也是团结一心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:42.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但渐渐出现了倒戈到神明一方的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:47.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,或是放弃战斗而隔岸观火的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:52.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是现在所谓的调和势力和旁观势力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:10:00.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后我们也开始被称为混沌势力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:06.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他们认为我们会让世界陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:12.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,战斗数百年然后休养数百年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:17.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就在这种形势下  那孩子降生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名为托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名字取自这个世界的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:29.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔的名字居然是来自我们这个世界的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:38.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这个男人从以前就通过预知书籍的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后在我们的世界贩卖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是盗版作家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,作家死后经过一段时间就会丧失著作权对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:55.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那么在书写成之前  在其他世界出版也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:58.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毕竟没有研究费就活不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,董事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:06.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类是我们当时压根没放在眼里的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:12.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是有时觉得很有趣或是会做些有趣的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只有这种程度的认知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然他们之中也有崇拜神明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:25.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是作为敌对势力而言和龙无法相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以就这么放着不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不过当人类和调和势力沆瀣一气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混沌势力中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:42.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也开始有族人鼓吹人类是祸害  应该消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:47.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸  人类是怎样的存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是祸害罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,应该消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当时我认为如果不迎合势力的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:58.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔会受到迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.66,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:05.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔自出生起就被划分到我们混沌派
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我意识到她不得不背负着作为我女儿的重担
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,毁灭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我觉得这并不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,产生这样想法的我也许是被人类所影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:26.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,于是我决定让托尔自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:30.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,让她游历四方  接触不同的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,希望她能拥有自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔积极学习自己感兴趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混沌势力对于人类的轻蔑态度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我估计她应该很快就会对此产生疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:49.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是托尔她暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,暴走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:57.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她单骑闯入神明的阵营
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,于是流落到了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:05.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后就遇到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我也感到非常震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:15.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类与龙之间居然产生了如此强韧的牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我完全没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是托尔为什么会做出这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:28.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔比任何人都渴望结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,「若是能打败神明便能结束战争」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她一定是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:43.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多就是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,细节还是去问托尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能告诉我一件事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我刚遇上托尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔说她已然是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,您觉得会是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:05.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不甚解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也推测不出托尔的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,若是对照人类的价值观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我便不是个合格的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我倒觉得你已经挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔要战斗并没有遵从势力的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而是托尔独自一人决定的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:30.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然刚开始每条龙都是这样过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好了  该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,姑且重申一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我绝不认可你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:49.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,别看他这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:54.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其实和这边的神明都疏通好关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:56.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,关于托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:01.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在你寿终正寝之前都给我好生照料她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的  我会照料好她的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:32.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天托尔的爸爸来公司了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他告诉我关于托尔来到这个世界之前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:48.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后如果你觉得可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比如为什么托尔会想来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:57.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要是愿意  我想听托尔你自己说说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,当然  不是在强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是不想说也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:08.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能变成人类模样的魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,第一次就成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.75,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(957.486,882.657)}托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然你是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,「去游遍不同的地方吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你的父亲是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:39.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,终焉帝是想让女儿成为旁观势力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:45.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就这样踏上了旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今天也在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,领土啊  权力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,总是以这些为理由发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然也会造出些有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:09.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人类给龙的印象就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:14.05,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\3c&HB26CF1&\pos(965.6,858.943)}康娜卡姆依
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:13.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托乌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托乌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是康娜  你为什么要变成人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因为人类的手能做很多精细活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:29.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是上一代的康娜卡姆依吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要做什么样的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,收集虫子来吓他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只是想让他多看下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因为忙于战争准备而没有多余的精力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明过几百年才会有一次战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,战争真是讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.39,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\3c&HD5508E&\pos(978.171,895.514)\4c&H364654&}魁札尔科亚特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,魁札尔科亚特尔  你个懦弱之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,明明拥有很强的实力却不参与斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我讨厌战争哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,从旁观者的视角来看  战争毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔君不如别当混沌势力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是混沌势力代表人物终焉帝的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,若是女儿叛逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,父亲的处境将会变糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.13,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,868.333)\3c&H953F3E&\fad(700,0)}法夫纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无法随心所欲的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不配为龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,强行被划入派别也是徒增麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:42.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你明明是龙却过无法活得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,违我心意者格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,即便是亲生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这就是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,太极端了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:10.00,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&HED5C2A&\4c&H233159&\pos(966.667,893.556)}艾尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我已经跟你过不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:09.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在此分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:11.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,派别不同吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你说的话确实有一定的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:20.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可能我不过是在被人利用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:24.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我不认为这是愚蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,祈祷是崇高的神圣行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:30.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以救人于水火之时我会感到心情愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还能填肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:41.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你以自我之意志  与我一同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我对此感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我什么都选择不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:55.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢不自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,混沌势力什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,调和势力什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:03.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这不是我的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能吵架的关系才更让我适应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,虽然我尊重我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但身为终焉帝之女的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:16.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想要自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想要孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:26.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,为之而战来赢得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,无所谓势力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这是我一人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,消灭这帮神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,扯断所有关于龙的束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:37.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,变得自由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:39.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什么都没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的变成孤身一人的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我发现自己无事想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,孤身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,还挺可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我因恐惧自由而回缩的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是小林你将其温柔地牵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:21.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:25.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,这和毫无目的就来到东京的我挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,现在我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:31.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想成为女仆
